title: Top US spy says war in Ukraine will likely become 'more unpredictable and escalatory'
content:
1. Top US spy says war in Ukraine will likely become 'more unpredictable and escalatory'  CNN
  2. U.S. intelligence assesses Putin is preparing for "prolonged conflict" beyond eastern Ukraine  Axios
  3. Putin preparing for prolonged war in Ukraine, U.S spy chief says  Reuters
  4. Top intel official warns Putin's invasion could become 'more unpredictable and potentially escalatory'  POLITICO
  5. Putin seeking goals beyond Ukraine’s east: US intelligence chief  Al Jazeera English
